<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>인트라넷</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh; background: #f0f2f5;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif; color: #1a1f36;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1f36, #2d3561); color: #fff;
      padding: 0 32px; height: 60px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .header-left { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; }
    .header-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
    .user-info { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }

    .btn-logout {
      padding: 7px 16px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      border-radius: 8px; color: #fff; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-logout:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }

    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 16px; text-align: center; }

    .welcome { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .welcome span { color: #4f7cff; }
    .sub { color: #6b7280; font-size: 15px; }

    .cards {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px; margin-top: 48px;
    }

    .menu-card {
      background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .menu-card-link {
      opacity: 1; text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
      transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    }
    .menu-card-link:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    }

    .menu-icon {
      width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 14px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 16px; font-size: 26px;
    }

    .menu-card h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .menu-card p  { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="header-left">인트라넷</div>
  <div class="header-right">
    <span class="user-info"><%= user.name %> (<%= user.empNo %>)</span>
    <a class="btn-logout" href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <div class="welcome"><span><%= user.name %></span>님, 환영합니다!</div>
  <div class="sub">오늘도 좋은 하루 되세요.</div>

  <div class="cards">
    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="menu-icon" style="background:#ede9fe;">&#128203;</div>
      <h3>전자결재</h3><p>준비 중</p>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="menu-icon" style="background:#dbeafe;">&#128197;</div>
      <h3>일정관리</h3><p>준비 중</p>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="menu-icon" style="background:#dcfce7;">&#128226;</div>
      <h3>공지사항</h3><p>준비 중</p>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-card">
      <div class="menu-icon" style="background:#fef9c3;">&#128101;</div>
      <h3>사원 주소록</h3><p>준비 중</p>
    </div>
    <a class="menu-card menu-card-link" href="/mpoms/vesselci">
      <div class="menu-icon" style="background:#e0f2fe;">&#9875;</div>
      <h3>모선코드 등록</h3><p>MPOMS 코드관리</p>
    </a>
    <a class="menu-card menu-card-link" href="/club">
      <div class="menu-icon" style="background:#fce7f3;">&#127939;</div>
      <h3>동호회</h3><p>동호회 관리</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
